Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.29,0:00:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在瞬間明白所有真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.11,0:00:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要開始就不會停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.13,0:00:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下來的是路面電車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.73,0:00:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是意外 是事件 關係非常微妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.82,0:00:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看清唯一真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.51,0:00:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表看似小孩 頭腦卻是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.41,0:00:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字就是 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.43,0:01:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路面電車急刹車事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.90,0:01:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南怎麽這麽慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.03,0:01:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經5點40分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.57,0:01:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.03,0:01:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.28,0:01:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢啦 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.66,0:01:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.04,0:01:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.66,0:02:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然遲到了10分鍾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.71,0:02:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是睡過頭而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.29,0:02:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還說的這麽輕松
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.80,0:02:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米花樂園的新遊戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.30,0:02:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說要排很久的隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.43,0:02:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過現在過去的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.43,0:02:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該可以排到第一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.89,0:02:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 現在早上6點都不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.39,0:02:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開往米花樂園的車子就要來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.94,0:02:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險 請退到白線外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.40,0:02:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.66,0:02:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上車吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.92,0:02:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒 好像被我們包了一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.51,0:02:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有人會星期天一大早跑來坐電車的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.59,0:02:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽還沒來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.60,0:02:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢夥到底在搞什麽嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.39,0:03:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堀井常常遲到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.39,0:03:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過連清水也遲到就太奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.35,0:03:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人 今天只有你一個嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.19,0:03:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 還有兩個還沒來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.57,0:03:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問有什麽事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.44,0:03:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在車子裏面拍照無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.99,0:03:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 請別打擾到其牠客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.94,0:03:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.53,0:03:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於趕上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.83,0:03:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽這麽慢 清水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.04,0:03:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 川崎學長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.62,0:03:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我睡過頭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.38,0:03:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堀井學長呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.71,0:03:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.25,0:03:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他每次都是最後關頭才會出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.71,0:03:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那差不多就到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.63,0:03:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲差不多時間就要開車了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.92,0:03:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.14,0:03:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.01,0:03:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.77,0:03:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我遲到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.77,0:03:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.69,0:03:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都這樣遲到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.70,0:03:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.03,0:04:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這比駕駛遊戲還要有魄力啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.87,0:04:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 實物的確不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.92,0:04:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐們也要去米花樂園嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.07,0:04:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.67,0:04:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們花山大學的鐵道研究會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.38,0:04:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是來拍攝路面電車的照片的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.30,0:04:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路面電車近年越來越少了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.85,0:04:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢業後我要到德國留學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.94,0:04:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想趁現在拍些照片留作紀念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.90,0:04:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.98,0:04:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.86,0:04:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看川崎學長那種樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.65,0:04:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只有照相的技術是專傢級的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.78,0:04:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 清水 什麽只有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.53,0:04:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.04,0:04:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一站是針井神社前 針井神社前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.38,0:04:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.09,0:04:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(要下車的乘客請按下按鈕)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.45,0:04:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要下車了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.30,0:05:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 前面不遠有個很棒的拍攝地點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.06,0:05:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很棒的拍攝地點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.43,0:05:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綁上兩個結應該問題了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.10,0:05:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 堀井 清水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.15,0:05:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這相機箱是新買的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.15,0:05:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裏面還有新的照相機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.07,0:05:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要讓人亂碰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.86,0:05:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 拜託你了 川崎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.91,0:05:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拍出好的作品啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.08,0:05:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.46,0:05:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多要開車了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.93,0:05:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.77,0:05:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 總算趕上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.91,0:06:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.99,0:06:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川崎學長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.70,0:06:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電車已經出發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.41,0:06:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 這邊也準備好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.96,0:06:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.59,0:06:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那堀井學長我們也到後面去拍攝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.96,0:06:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.96,0:06:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.63,0:07:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川崎學長 你沒受傷吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.56,0:07:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 只是嚇了一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.51,0:07:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 不要胡鬧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.23,0:07:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有緊急刹車你可能就死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.40,0:07:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.27,0:07:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥 爲什麽會掉到鐵軌上呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.90,0:07:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我站在那梯子上面拍攝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.03,0:07:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來那梯子突然倒下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.53,0:07:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得梯子四只腳都固定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.83,0:07:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麽痕蹟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.42,0:07:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個地方也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.42,0:07:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.55,0:07:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是S掛鈎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.52,0:07:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還綁著鋼琴線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.77,0:07:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這該不會是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.65,0:08:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.57,0:08:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.95,0:08:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大傢上電車吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.41,0:08:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.53,0:08:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 你在做什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.91,0:08:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電車要開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.83,0:08:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.50,0:08:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 大傢都上車了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.21,0:08:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大傢都上來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.67,0:08:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要元太上了車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.92,0:08:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就到齊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.62,0:08:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.26,0:08:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽意思啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.80,0:08:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.48,0:08:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堀井學長 怎麽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.69,0:08:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 堀井 你在做什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.61,0:08:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別碰他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.16,0:08:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.61,0:08:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別碰他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.82,0:08:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麽意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.20,0:08:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車長 請報警
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.00,0:08:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報警 這是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.16,0:08:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難...難道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.36,0:09:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已經死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.88,0:09:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.59,0:09:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屍體前額腫了一塊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.01,0:09:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後腦有個裂傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.98,0:09:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相機箱上面有血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.65,0:09:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地闆有血蹟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.36,0:09:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.57,0:09:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者是堀井正雄先生 22歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.95,0:09:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屍體前額有血腫 後腦有裂傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.83,0:09:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想致命傷應該是後腦的裂傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.50,0:09:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 我是針井署的若井刑事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.88,0:09:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不可以說一下死者堀井先生死亡前的情形呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.38,0:09:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在車頭看掉到鐵軌上的川崎先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.68,0:09:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲緊急刹車我忙著站穩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.93,0:09:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以什麽也沒看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.06,0:10:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我因爲很害怕 所以閉著眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.65,0:10:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一直看著前面發生的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.94,0:10:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以什麽也沒看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.94,0:10:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和堀井學長在電車後面攝影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.66,0:10:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來因爲突然緊急刹車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.45,0:10:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以飛到前面去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.25,0:10:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後堀井學長怎樣我就不知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.54,0:10:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.67,0:10:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我緊急將電車給刹車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.55,0:10:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上跑到下面去看那年輕人的情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.05,0:10:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以對死者就...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.01,0:10:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.10,0:10:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大傢都跑到車子外面去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.64,0:10:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有其牠人跑到車廂裏面呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.23,0:10:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下車也只有幾分鍾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.52,0:10:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒看到其牠人上車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.82,0:10:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.32,0:10:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被害者後腦的裂傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.28,0:10:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和相機箱的血蹟來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.61,0:10:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堀井先生因爲緊急刹車所以失去平衡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.45,0:11:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒下去的時候後腦撞到了相機箱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.90,0:11:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.63,0:11:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個很單純的意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.07,0:11:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣說太奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.39,0:11:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏奇怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.01,0:11:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將來要成爲警視廳本部長的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.47,0:11:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會判斷錯誤的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.31,0:11:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子的你知道些什麽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.64,0:11:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要成爲什麽是你的自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.98,0:11:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是少年偵探團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.40,0:11:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 我們是名偵探毛利小五郎的弟子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.24,0:11:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.74,0:11:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽 那個有名的"沈睡的小五郎"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.12,0:11:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏有問題呢 小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.04,0:11:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那看看這相機箱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.58,0:11:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箱子下面有很多血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.13,0:11:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是從上面撞到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.88,0:11:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是上面會有很多血啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.97,0:11:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.80,0:11:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指這個啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.34,0:11:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大概是因爲緊急刹車所以箱子倒了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.89,0:12:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過箱子綁在扶手上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.56,0:12:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不會動的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.15,0:12:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這帶子...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.65,0:12:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得那個時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.90,0:12:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綁上兩個結應該就沒問題了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.28,0:12:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 堀井 清水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.20,0:12:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這相機箱是新買的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.17,0:12:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.45,0:12:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那條帶子我下車之前綁上兩個結的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.87,0:12:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲這是新買的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.66,0:12:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以叫他們都不要去亂碰的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.21,0:12:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 連旁邊也爛掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.45,0:12:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麽說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.64,0:12:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是有人把箱子從扶手上解開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.22,0:12:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.52,0:12:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從後面被撞到 前額卻有血腫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.06,0:12:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得很奇怪嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.56,0:12:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.40,0:12:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你看那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.57,0:12:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏有一大灘血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.95,0:12:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是被打...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.86,0:12:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這不太可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.70,0:13:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在緊急刹車時要作案是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.88,0:13:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了意外別無其牠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.29,0:13:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 一定是意外沒有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.17,0:13:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.79,0:13:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.67,0:13:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.17,0:13:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在電線杆旁的S掛鈎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.84,0:13:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有相機箱側面的傷痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.05,0:13:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.97,0:13:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然在緊急刹車中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.93,0:13:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本不可能的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.77,0:13:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這並不是意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.98,0:13:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堀井先生是被殺死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.19,0:13:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且犯人就在這些人裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.02,0:13:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車長 電車不能一直停在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.00,0:13:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要做詳細的調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.75,0:13:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不可以把牠開回車庫去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.11,0:13:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.71,0:13:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 電車回車庫之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.30,0:13:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上叫署裏的人去調查 你去通知他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.22,0:14:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.18,0:14:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蹧了 一定要搞定這年輕的警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.10,0:14:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 在大傢的面前不能使用蔴醉槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.64,0:14:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這電車裏面也沒地方可以躲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.77,0:14:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.02,0:14:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川崎先生 清水小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.90,0:14:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於堀井先生意外死亡事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.78,0:14:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須寫報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.03,0:14:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請跟我們回局裏去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.57,0:14:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.74,0:14:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.45,0:14:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朋友們也可以一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.08,0:14:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.16,0:14:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 警察先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.17,0:14:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麽事 小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.13,0:14:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也會找你錄口供的 放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.88,0:14:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.46,0:14:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才在倒下的梯子旁邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.51,0:14:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我撿到了這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.14,0:14:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大概和這事件有關係吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.39,0:14:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這S掛鈎和堀井先生死亡到底有什麽關係呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.44,0:14:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲如果這架子沒倒的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.31,0:14:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電車就不會緊急刹車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.57,0:14:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎麽...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.82,0:15:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 把那掛鈎給我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.12,0:15:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 警察先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.95,0:15:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.71,0:15:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全吻合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.42,0:15:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然這和上面的傷痕完全吻合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.92,0:15:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這掛鈎是掛在架子上面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.09,0:15:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這斷掉的鋼琴線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.09,0:15:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若井警官 關於鋼琴線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.72,0:15:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一些卷在電車的安全杆上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.72,0:15:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽 給我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.72,0:15:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 就是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.14,0:15:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粗細 材質 切口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.48,0:15:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是一樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.94,0:15:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小弟弟 這S掛鈎是在哪裏找到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.03,0:15:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就掛在這電線杆的鐵圈上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.49,0:15:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.78,0:15:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這鐵圈上面的痕蹟是新的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.79,0:15:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想那裏應該也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.83,0:15:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 這裏也有痕蹟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.79,0:15:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有對面正好有個招牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.38,0:16:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果真如我所料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.05,0:16:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.34,0:16:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這招牌柱子下有一些殘留的鋼琴線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.26,0:16:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麽說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.02,0:16:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被勾在架子上的S掛鈎的鋼琴線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.94,0:16:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繞過附件的電線杆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.61,0:16:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再繞過約50公尺遠的電線杆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.94,0:16:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再綁到對面招牌的柱子上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.20,0:16:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後開過來的電車拉扯鋼琴線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.33,0:16:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,架子倒下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.83,0:16:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面的人失去平衡而倒下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.00,0:16:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,架子是故意被弄倒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.04,0:16:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過到底是誰的惡作劇呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.00,0:16:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想架子倒下的事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.26,0:16:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有堀井先生死亡的事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.51,0:16:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該都有關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.22,0:16:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 就是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.51,0:16:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在讓我若井警官將這事件的方式給解開吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.39,0:16:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 上電車去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.89,0:17:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.24,0:17:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大傢準備好了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.90,0:17:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堀井先生並不是意外死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.16,0:17:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被殺害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.50,0:17:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 你剛才說是意外死亡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.12,0:17:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 而且井崎先生的架子那事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.34,0:17:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道是有人故意做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.76,0:17:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麽你的意思是說有人要殺我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.22,0:17:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 有這個可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.14,0:17:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麽回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.89,0:17:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只堀井學長的死不是意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.85,0:17:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有川崎學長從架子上掉下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.35,0:17:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是有人故意做的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.90,0:17:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些我現在正要開始說明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.32,0:17:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是殺害堀井先生的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.69,0:17:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果犯人知道會有有緊急刹車的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.45,0:17:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 如果可以故意把川崎先生的架子給拉倒的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.62,0:17:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只有一點時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.25,0:17:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能殺死堀井先生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.79,0:18:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川崎先生掉下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.25,0:18:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大傢的註意都集中的前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.30,0:18:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後犯人就利用川崎的相機箱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.38,0:18:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往堀井後腦打下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.18,0:18:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後被打的堀井就往前倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.68,0:18:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撞到了扶手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.72,0:18:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再摔倒地上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.56,0:18:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下一大灘血液
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.56,0:18:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然犯人馬上把箱子綁回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.82,0:18:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過太緊急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.07,0:18:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只打了一個結
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.28,0:18:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後就出現緊急刹車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.33,0:18:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堀井先生就這樣滑過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.20,0:18:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就撞到箱子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.75,0:18:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時在車上距離堀井先生最近的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.25,0:18:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你吧 清水小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.67,0:18:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.34,0:18:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次的緊急刹車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.30,0:18:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差點害我以爲會死呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.22,0:18:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車長先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.68,0:18:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這電車之前應該還有其牠電車通過吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.85,0:19:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在5點40分左右應該有一輛通過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.98,0:19:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說犯人在5點40分之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.57,0:19:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才將鋼琴線給裝上去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.11,0:19:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還知道川崎先生會在這個地方拍照的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.24,0:19:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天我和堀井 清水三人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.79,0:19:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定在這裏攝影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.12,0:19:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,架子是今天早上去車站前才擺上去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.29,0:19:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我在5點54分的時候就已經到達針井車站了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.92,0:19:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這裏到針井車站大概有4公裏吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.88,0:19:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是自行車10分鍾就可到達了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.14,0:19:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且電車離開針井神社的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.56,0:19:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清水小姐用手機打電話給川崎先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.10,0:19:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是爲了確認川崎先生的確站在架子上面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.94,0:19:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道...真的是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.61,0:19:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又沒有去碰你的相機箱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.61,0:19:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有殺害堀井學長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.11,0:19:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你有什麽證據呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.16,0:19:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,證據 這...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.08,0:20:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有證據就懷疑別人是犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.25,0:20:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清水小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.79,0:20:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的手掌和手表上面的傷痕是怎麽回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.59,0:20:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傷痕關你什麽事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.05,0:20:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.47,0:20:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相機箱上面的血蹟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.89,0:20:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該就是你手上流出來的血吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.44,0:20:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你用箱子打堀井先生的時候弄傷的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.15,0:20:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.48,0:20:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果拿去化驗之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.44,0:20:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還敢這麽說嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.07,0:20:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化驗的報告上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.41,0:20:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箱子右上角的血液
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.24,0:20:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經確認不是堀井先生的血液了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.08,0:20:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且上面還能找到不是川崎先生和堀井先生的指紋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.21,0:20:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麽樣 清水小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.10,0:20:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清水 你爲什麽要殺堀井
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.01,0:21:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我和堀井正在交往
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.56,0:21:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經談婚論嫁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.02,0:21:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 因爲他要到德國去留學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.07,0:21:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我說要和他一起去的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.49,0:21:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我不能帶你去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.41,0:21:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爲爸爸在那邊幫我訂下婚姻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.74,0:21:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要過去結婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.33,0:21:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.71,0:21:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法原諒他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.84,0:21:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個堀井 我實在無法原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.73,0:23:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年偵探團 辛苦你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.86,0:23:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爲了紀念就讓我替你們簽名吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.15,0:23:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年偵探團將電車事故和殺人事件的謎題給解開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.54,0:23:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜啓 若井健兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.50,0:23:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位少年偵探團 下次再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.01,0:23:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好阩官的時候也別像這樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.95,0:24:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通常會有人去攻擊正在打電話的人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.87,0:24:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道 計劃著殺人事件的是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.98,0:24:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.45,0:24:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本廳刑事戀愛物語 (前篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.96,0:24:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.57,0:24:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電動運動車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.59,0:24:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集那個人將以警察身份登場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.42,0:24:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.20,0:00:18.15,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開所有雜誌還是不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.50,0:00:22.12,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能在這搖頭歎息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.38,0:00:26.48,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒有適合我的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.63,0:00:30.54,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世紀末的流行色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.85,0:00:34.59,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都無法討得你的歡心 惹得你滿腔怒火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.77,0:00:38.38,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很抱歉如臨深淵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.52,0:00:43.22,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像走在懸崖邊緣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.69,0:00:47.35,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搖搖慾墜的感覺有什麽不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.47,0:00:51.34,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這樣也一定要嚮前走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.74,0:00:56.01,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男子漢 一點也不是問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.96,0:01:05.06,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不到緊要關頭不出手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.17,0:01:08.86,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 不要用冷淡的眼光看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.05,0:01:12.68,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我用自己的速度前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.05,0:01:16.91,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則我馬上會崩潰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.39,0:01:20.91,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像走在懸崖邊緣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.40,0:01:24.88,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搖搖慾墜的感覺有什麽不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.32,0:01:29.42,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這樣也一定要嚮前走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.74,0:01:34.05,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男子漢 一點也不是問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.93,0:21:55.57,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這孕育著神秘的夜裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.10,0:22:00.24,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請閉上眼睛 獻上你的祈禱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.02,0:22:06.58,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這月光融融的夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.15,0:22:13.00,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽說我們因爲愛而生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.50,0:22:24.27,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 一切都停滯不前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.88,0:22:30.56,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼看未來化爲碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.84,0:22:39.27,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 赤著腳 踩在大地上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.39,0:22:44.70,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跨越彩虹 抓住天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.48,0:22:51.22,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我祈禱 抓住胸前的十字架 在白天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.36,0:22:57.54,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望照燿著你 在夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.66,0:23:03.72,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫暖的光芒 將你擁抱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.87,0:23:10.46,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠爲你停留 爲你的愛而停留
